title: Cars, Cops and Criminals - S01E01 - 9th July 2008
description:
Cars, Cops and Criminals

Big Business
New three-part series examining the changing face of car theft. Car crime has become a sophisticated business stretching across continents and costing the country tens of millions of pounds. The programme accompanies the Metropolitan Police&#039;s Stolen Vehicle Unit to Cyprus, one of the biggest destinations for stolen cars from Britain. It also follows Barry, a car-crime bounty hunter, as he searches for stolen vehicles, and talks to a mother in Kensington who had her car stolen at gunpoint.
